data.description: This super cute 3bed/2bath split level home sits on a well-manicured corner lot and has been lovingly cared for by long term owner. Features large finished lower-level room perfect for relaxing with the family or can be a fourth bedroom, as it's directly across from the second full bath. This home is perfect for entertaining and enjoying the charming neighborhood.  Walking distance to Country Club Hills Amphitheater, nearby schools, and local shopping. Easy access to neighboring suburbs and downtown Chicago via I-294 and I-57. Freshly painted, cosmetic updates, new fixtures, newer wireless garage door opener, includes all kitchen appliances, washer/dryer and central air.  Perfect starter home at this price! Property is vacant, ready for a quick close and being sold AS-IS. Enjoy your first summer BBQ in your new home!
